# Gorny, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Gorny () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Kabansky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 159 as of 2010.
Geography
Gorny is located  southwest of Kabansk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Posolskaya is the nearest rural locality.
